<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bnʿyr ạ̹blys wjnwdh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (bnʿyr ạ̹blys wjnwdh .. tḥt rjlynạ mndạs
 nzʿ wfk lkl qywdh .. nʿln llsẖʿb ạlkẖlạṣ)2
 ạlqrạr- (ḍạmnyn hạnʿdy byk .. dạ ạnt qạỷd msẖwạrnạ
 ạ̉frạḥnạ mʿạk btzyd .. frḥ ạlrb qwtnạ)2
 2- (wsṭ ḥrwbnạ ṣạr ạ̉ʿdạỷnạ .. kẖbz lynạ yạ jbạr
 kl sẖʿwbnạ wkl blạdnạ .. ṣạrt mskn lyk yạ bạr)2
 3- (bnʿly rạyạt lmsyḥnạ .. rạfʿyn ạsmh lyl wnhạr
 yẓhr ḥqh wbtsbyḥnạ .. nksẖf nʿln kl stạr)2</lyrics>
<author>hrmạs smyr, hrmạs smyr</author>
<hymn_number>592</hymn_number>
</song>